RealTimeResultGroupDefinition.SqlString: SELECT Port.Name AS 'Port Name', AllDevice.Name AS 'Device Name', IgmpHostResults.McastCompatibilityMode AS 'Multicast Version', IgmpHostResults.HostState AS 'Host State', SUM(IgmpHostResults.TxFrameCount) AS 'Tx Frames', SUM(IgmpHostResults.RxFrameCount) AS 'Rx Frames', SUM(IgmpHostResults.RxUnknownTypeCount) AS 'Rx Unknown Types', SUM(IgmpHostResults.RxIgmpCheckSumErrorCount) AS 'Rx IGMP Checksum Errors', SUM(IgmpHostResults.RxIgmpLengthErrorCount) AS 'Rx IGMP Length Errors' FROM AllDevice, Port, IgmpHostResults, IgmpHostConfig, RelationTable WHERE ( RelationTable.Type = 'AffiliationPort' AND RelationTable.SourceHnd = AllDevice.Handle AND RelationTable.TargetHnd = Port.Handle AND IgmpHostConfig.ParentHnd = AllDevice.Handle AND IgmpHostResults.ParentHnd = IgmpHostConfig.Handle AND IgmpHostResults.IfHandle = IgmpHostConfig.IfHandle AND AllDevice.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND Port.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND IgmpHostResults.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND IgmpHostConfig.DataSetId = @DataSetId AND RelationTable.DataSetId = @DataSetId ) GROUP BY IgmpHostResults.IfHandle
